{
  "sequenceId": "support",
  "name": "Customer Support",
  "description": "Help users troubleshoot issues and find solutions",
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "text": "Hi there! I'm here to help you with any issues you're experiencing.",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 1000,
      "nextMessageId": 2,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "What type of problem are you having today?",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 1500,
      "nextMessageId": 3,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "sender": "user",
      "storeKey": "support.issue_type",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "App won't start",
          "nextMessageId": 10
        },
        {
          "text": "Login problems",
          "nextMessageId": 20
        },
        {
          "text": "Feature not working",
          "nextMessageId": 30
        },
        {
          "text": "Other issue",
          "nextMessageId": 40
        }
      ],
      "type": "choice"
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "text": "I understand how frustrating startup issues can be. Let's troubleshoot this step by step.",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 1500,
      "nextMessageId": 11,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "text": "First, have you tried restarting your device completely?",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 1500,
      "nextMessageId": 12,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "sender": "user",
      "storeKey": "support.tried_restart",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Yes, still not working",
          "nextMessageId": 13
        },
        {
          "text": "No, let me try that",
          "nextMessageId": 14
        }
      ],
      "type": "choice"
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "text": "Let's check if you have the latest version. Please update the app from your app store.",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 2000,
      "nextMessageId": 15,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "text": "Please restart your device and try opening the app again. This fixes most startup issues!",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 2000,
      "nextMessageId": 60,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "text": "If updating doesn't help, try clearing the app's cache or reinstalling it.",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 2000,
      "nextMessageId": 60,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "text": "Login issues can be tricky. Let's figure out what's happening.",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 1500,
      "nextMessageId": 21,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "text": "Are you getting an error message when you try to log in?",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 1500,
      "nextMessageId": 22,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "sender": "user",
      "storeKey": "support.login_error",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Invalid credentials",
          "nextMessageId": 23
        },
        {
          "text": "Network error",
          "nextMessageId": 24
        },
        {
          "text": "App just freezes",
          "nextMessageId": 25
        }
      ],
      "type": "choice"
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "text": "Double-check your username and password. If you're sure they're correct, try resetting your password.",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 2500,
      "nextMessageId": 60,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "text": "Check your internet connection. Try switching between WiFi and mobile data to see if that helps.",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 2500,
      "nextMessageId": 60,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "text": "If the app freezes during login, try force-closing and reopening it, or restart your device.",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 2500,
      "nextMessageId": 60,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 1500,
      "storeKey": "support.broken_feature",
      "placeholderText": "Describe the feature that's not working...",
      "nextMessageId": 31,
      "type": "textInput"
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "text": "Thanks for letting me know about the issue with {support.broken_feature|that feature}.",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 1500,
      "nextMessageId": 32,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 1500,
      "storeKey": "support.feature_behavior",
      "placeholderText": "What exactly happens when you try to use it?",
      "nextMessageId": 33,
      "type": "textInput"
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "text": "I see. That behavior with {support.broken_feature|the feature} sounds unusual.",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 2000,
      "nextMessageId": 34,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "text": "Try logging out and back in, or updating the app. If it persists, our team will investigate.",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 2500,
      "nextMessageId": 60,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 1500,
      "storeKey": "support.custom_issue",
      "placeholderText": "Describe your issue in detail...",
      "nextMessageId": 41,
      "type": "textInput"
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "text": "Thank you for the detailed description. Let me see how I can help with that.",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 2000,
      "nextMessageId": 42,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "text": "Based on what you've described, here are some general troubleshooting steps:",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 1500,
      "nextMessageId": 43,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "text": "1. Restart the app\n2. Check for updates\n3. Restart your device\n4. Contact our support team if the issue persists",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 3000,
      "nextMessageId": 60,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "text": "Did this help resolve your issue?",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 1000,
      "nextMessageId": 61,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "sender": "user",
      "storeKey": "support.issue_resolved",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Yes, it's working now!",
          "nextMessageId": 70
        },
        {
          "text": "Still having problems",
          "nextMessageId": 80
        }
      ],
      "type": "choice"
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
      "text": "Wonderful! I'm glad we could get that sorted out for you.",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 1500,
      "nextMessageId": 71,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 71,
      "text": "If you run into any other issues, don't hesitate to reach out. We're always here to help!",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 2000,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 80,
      "text": "I'm sorry the issue persists. Let me connect you with our technical support team for further assistance.",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 2000,
      "nextMessageId": 81,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 81,
      "text": "They'll be able to provide more specialized help. You can reach them through the 'Contact Support' option in settings.",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 2500,
      "nextMessageId": 82,
      "type": "bot"
    },
    {
      "id": 82,
      "text": "Thank you for your patience, and we'll get this resolved for you soon!",
      "sender": "bot",
      "delay": 1500,
      "type": "bot"
    }
  ]
}